response.overview: Keisha Grey pulls a muscle in her groin, and calls physiotherapist Angela White desperate for help. The two arrange a home visit, but Angela forewarns her, this is going to be a vigorous and hands-on massage. Lena Paul instantly remembers her old tutor Zoey Monroe from high school when she walks into the spa. Lena's mind is flooded with happy memories and she chats away while the hot blonde client gets undressed. Latina masseuse Luna Star finds out her client Sara Luvv is also Latina but Sara doesn't speak or understand so Luna uses some very physical gestures to get the point across. Lyra Law gets off a stressful legal call in time for her standing appointment with sexy masseuse Kimmy Granger. No one is better at law than Lyra and no one is better at massaging than Kimmy!
response.title: Surrender Your Stress
